费尔节2“不存在”，当地旅游委员会声称https://www.nme.com/news/music/fyre-festival-2-does-not-exist-claim-local-tourism-board-3843239?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fyre-festival-2-does-not-exist-claim-local-tourism-boardAneesa Ahmed Mon, 03 Mar 2025 20:51:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3843239 <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fyre Festival创始人Billy McFarland在Fox News上。信用 - 西奥·沃戈（Theo Wargo）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们对此事件不了解，也不了解任何人或公司。对我们来说，这是一个不存在的事件”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fyre-festival-2-does-not-exist-claim-local-tourism-board-3843239">当地旅游委员会</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上，“不存在” Fyre节2“不存在”。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Fyre Festival创始人Billy McFarland在Fox News上。信用 - 西奥·沃戈（Theo Wargo）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Fyre-Festival-founder-Billy-McFarland-on-Fox-News.-Credit-Theo-Wargo-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Fyre Festival 2“不存在”根据墨西哥旅游局的官方声明，尽管这一事件声称这在社交媒体上是“真实的”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/festivals-blog/fyre-festival-luxury-chaos-pictures-2061836#TWfKse5rOmohkHUp.99">Fyre Festival：这是有史以来最糟糕的“豪华”节吗？</a></strong></li></ul><p>这是在音乐节及其创始人比利·麦克法兰（Billy McFarland）上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fyre-festival-2-announces-dates-location-and-tickets-for-real-return-3840999">宣布</a>，其“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fyre-festival-2-confirmed-for-2025-has-yet-to-book-any-artists-3792163">真实回报</a>”将于5月30日至6月2日在墨西哥坎昆的热带岛屿Isla Mujeres举行。门票本周开始销售，<a href="https://www.fyre.mx/explore">价格</a>从1,400美元到25,000美元不等。高级套餐的价格高达110万美元。</p><p>但是，此后，旅游委员会和地方官员声称不存在节日。伊斯拉·穆杰雷斯（Isla Mujeres）旅游局的<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2025/feb/27/fyre-festival-2-mexico"><em>《卫报》</em></a> （Edgar Gasca）在接受《卫报》（Guardian）讲话时说：“我们不了解这项活动，也不了解任何人或公司。对我们来说，这是不存在的事件。”</p><p>当加斯卡听到新闻时，加斯卡在哥伦比亚的波哥大参加了旅游博览会。他确认他已经与金塔纳鲁（Quintana Roo）州的旅游部长和被列为Fyre Festival 2的一部分的酒店进行了交谈，该活动没有接近。</p><p><em>卫报（Guardian）</em>向印象伊斯拉·穆耶雷斯（Isla Mujeres）伸出了印象，这是费尔承诺的豪华酒店之一，该酒店声称该酒店没有收到“对活动的任何方法或询问”，并且正在调查。</p><p>加斯卡说：“组织者甚至没有费力地接近当局。” “这很奇怪，因为任何经理都知道，如果您要举办活动，更不用说大规模的活动，您需要市政授权。</p><p>加斯卡补充说：“我认为他们认为他们只会宣布它，看看它是否受到关注，然后索要路途中途的许可证。” “这是一种天真的思考方式。”</p><p>上周，音乐节上了社交媒体宣布其回报，并在冗长的帖子中形容自己是“真实的”。</p><p>它将自己称为“为期三天的逃往墨西哥加勒比海地区，您将每天与您最喜欢的人才一起探索，并在晚上聚在一起与音乐一起庆祝”。 Fyre Festival 2还声称，它将以“由国际和当地人才领导的冒险活动，每天将客人乘坐边界进行游览，并在夜间团结私密的海滩表演”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGdUf2lxOab/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541